<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      /* Email styles need to be inline */
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <% images = ["https://theteenmagazine.s3.amazonaws.com/giphy.gif", "http://s3.amazonaws.com/theteenmagazine/Users/miajohansson/Desktop/ttm/blog/public/ckeditor_assets/pictures/2/content_3ZJ5ZIO.gif", "http://s3.amazonaws.com/theteenmagazine/Users/miajohansson/Desktop/ttm/blog/public/ckeditor_assets/pictures/1/content_giphy-1.gif"] %>
    <p>Hi <%= @pitch.title %>,</p>
    <p>Your interview <%= link_to @post.title, @post, style: "color: #4ABEB6;" %> was just published!</p>
    <% if @pitch.platform_to_share.present? && (!@pitch.platform_to_share.eql? "None selected") %>
      <p>
        We kindly request that you share the article link using <%= indefinite_articlerize(@pitch.platform_to_share) %> <b><%= @pitch.platform_to_share&.chomp('(preferred)')&.sub('w/', 'with') %></b> and reply to this email once you have done so.
        If you are no longer able to share the link or prefer to use a different platform, please inform us via email.
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <img style="display: block; max-width: 100%; width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;" src=<%= images[rand(0..2)] %>>
    <% end %>
    <p>We greatly appreciate interviewing, and featuring, you on The Teen Magazine! If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to send us an email. Congratulations!</p>
    <p>Best Regards,<br/>
      Mia Johansson</p>
  </body>
</html>
